beer.beer_description:
An aroma dominated by juicy grapefruit blended with Mosaic & Centennial hops gives a complex bouquet of pine resin & citrus peel.

The first sip is all about the juicy grapefruit, providing a bold & assertive flavour that balances perfectly with the floral piney hop bitterness. A subtle malt sweetness compliments the lot for a smooth & creamy mouthfeel... Peel and enjoy!
